[section#lex.charset
    [:en] Character sets
    [:zh_CN] 字符集
]

[%:begin#character.set
    [:en] character set
    [:zh_CN] 字符集
]

[para]
[:en]
The [+:adj translation[!character set]] consists of the following elements:
[:zh_CN]
[+:adj 翻译[!字符集]]由下列元素构成：

[list]
[item]
[:en]
each character named by ISO/IEC 10646, as identified by its unique UCS scalar
value, and
[:zh_CN]
ISO/IEC 10646 所指名的每个字符，识别为唯一 UCS 标量值，以及
[item]
[:en]
a distinct character for each UCS scalar value where no named character is
assigned.
[:zh_CN]
未被赋予具名字符的每个 UCS 标量值的一个单独字符。
[list:end]

[begin:note]
[:en]
ISO/IEC 10646 code points are integers in the range [$`[0, \mathrm{10FFFF}`]]
(hexadecimal).
[:zh_CN]
ISO/IEC 10646 代码点为范围 [$`[0, \mathrm{10FFFF}`]]（十六进制）中的整数。

[:en]
A surrogate code point is a value in the range [$`[\mathrm{D800}, \mathrm{DFFF}`]]
(hexadecimal).
[:zh_CN]
代用代码点为范围 [$`[\mathrm{D800}, \mathrm{DFFF}`]]（十六进制）中的值。

[:en]
A UCS scalar value is any code point that is not a surrogate code point.
[:zh_CN]
UCS 标量值为除代用代码点之外的任何代码点。
[end:note]

[para]
[:en]
[+:adj basic[!character set]] is a subset of the translation character set,
consisting of 96 characters as specified in [#:tab#lex.charset.basic].
[:zh_CN]
[+:adj 基本[!字符集]]为翻译字符集的子集，由 [#:tab#lex.charset.basic] 中指定的
96 个字符构成。

[begin:note]
[:en]
Unicode short names are given only as a means to identifying the character;
the numerical value has no other meaning in this context.
[:zh_CN]
Unicode 短名字只是为了识别字符而给出的一种方法；其数值在这个语境中没有其他意义。
[end:note]

